Class Param2itemMatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.viatra.query.runtime.internal.apiimpl.QueryResultWrapper

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.eclipse.viatra.query.runtime.api.ViatraQueryMatcher<Param2itemMatch>

    public class Param2itemMatcher
extends org.eclipse.viatra.query.runtime.api.impl.BaseMatcher<Param2itemMatch>
    Generated pattern matcher API of the org.eclipse.viatra.addon.viewers.runtime.model.patterns.param2item pattern, providing pattern-specific query methods.

    Use the pattern matcher on a given model via on(ViatraQueryEngine), e.g. in conjunction with ViatraQueryEngine#on(Notifier).

    Matches of the pattern will be represented as Param2itemMatch.

    Original source: 

     @QueryExplorer(checked = false)
 pattern param2item(param, trace : Trace, item : Item) {
        Trace.params(trace, param);
        Trace.targets(trace, item);
 } or {
        Trace.objects(trace, param);
        Trace.targets(trace, item);
 }
    See Also:
    Param2itemMatch, Param2itemProcessor, Param2itemQuerySpecification
